<div id="review_188779509" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/188779509" />
    <a title="Emily Ann" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5868571-emily-ann"><img alt="Emily Ann" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1347290972p2/5868571.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/188779509?book_show_action=true">Jul 24, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Emily Ann" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Emily Ann" href="/user/show/5868571-emily-ann">Emily Ann</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5868571-emily-ann?shelf=young-adult-kids">young-adult-kids</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5868571-emily-ann?shelf=spec-fic">spec-fic</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer188779509" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16783693904997758432">I wanted to like this, but I thought that the author tried to do too many things in too short of a book and it came out jumpy and disjointed. It is a very quick read (even for YA books), so perfectly worth it if you are interested in the concept. However, while I felt like I was shown some brief flashes of insights into characters/back stories/etc, they never followed through. I was left feeling like I walked through the middle of a conversation and never understood what was really happening.<br/><br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

