    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2583811230" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2583811230" />
    <a title="Erika" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/15190824-erika"><img alt="Erika" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1519063773p2/15190824.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2583811230?book_show_action=true">Nov 06, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Erika" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Erika" href="/user/show/15190824-erika">Erika</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2583811230" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3433049606074610096">I would&apos;ve loved this book if I had read it when I was younger. However, as someone who is suppose to be all grown up now, I can still appreciate a nice, quick read about a small town and the three kids who dream about leaving it and go on an adventure together. I&apos;m not immune to children&apos;s books, especially if it&apos;s related to water, the sea, the ocean, all the different and beautiful shades of blue.</span>
  <span id="freeText3433049606074610096" style="display:none">I would've loved this book if I had read it when I was younger. However, as someone who is suppose to be all grown up now, I can still appreciate a nice, quick read about a small town and the three kids who dream about leaving it and go on an adventure together. I'm not immune to children's books, especially if it's related to water, the sea, the ocean, all the different and beautiful shades of blue.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3433049606074610096" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


