<span id="freeTextContainer7966738828509235563">Short and sweet MG or YA novella. While I didn&apos;t think it was &quot;great&quot; it was a nice little &quot;feel good&quot; read. This is my first time reading a YA book by Alice Hoffman, although I have read her adult novels, and enjoyed them. </span>
  <span id="freeText7966738828509235563" style="display:none">Short and sweet MG or YA novella. While I didn't think it was "great" it was a nice little "feel good" read. This is my first time reading a YA book by Alice Hoffman, although I have read her adult novels, and enjoyed them. </span>
