<span id="freeTextContainer2187196533964021539">I really liked this book and am considering reading more of Hoffman&apos;s books. I like how the characters are relatable in many aspects of their life. The story was very interesting but I could see this as a one time read, but I do recommend!</span>
  <span id="freeText2187196533964021539" style="display:none">I really liked this book and am considering reading more of Hoffman's books. I like how the characters are relatable in many aspects of their life. The story was very interesting but I could see this as a one time read, but I do recommend!</span>
